+  // Allocate the instance:
+  //  If TLAB is enabled:
+  //    Try to allocate in the TLAB.
+  //    If fails, go to the slow path.
+  //    Initialize the allocation.
+  //    Exit.
+  //
+  //  Go to slow path.
